www/chromium compiles find with clang and gcc, but inspector doesn't work.
It opens dock that is all white and empty. Close button doesn't work either.

I have this problem for quite some time, but I was hoping it was some small regression, that would be fixed soon.

I had sane problem on FreeBSD-8-stable

Options: 
        CLANG: on
        CODECS: on
        DEBUG: off
        GCC46: off
        GCONF: on
        PULSEAUDIO: off


